Interface FrameworkSupportModel

  • All Superinterfaces:
    UserDataHolder
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    FrameworkSupportModelBase, FrameworkSupportModelImpl

    public interface FrameworkSupportModel
extends UserDataHolder
    Represents a state of 'Add Support for Frameworks' UI which may be shown inside 'New Project/Module' wizards and 'Add Framework Support' action
